{"type": "article", "id": 20301, "title": "带褶皱的茶具", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-06T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153737hv0Q5Ztkw1gUMJrX.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套浅粉色的茶具带有特别的褶皱，类似于花瓣或叶子。茶杯的一头像是捏在一起了，可以当做壶嘴来倒水，也可以做把手。托盘也有一个微微波浪，正好空缺了一个手提的位置。设计师从波斯一带的粘土灯中获得灵感，通过 3D 打印完成，售价 85 美元，<a href=\"http://www.bradleylbowers.com/shop/fhstqzhus3h1hxcjnc6gw2ehikdfrz\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153735boBD1rafqTRVC9tA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153736VJpiCgce0SErWOko.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153736JSVX2Abgy7INaUPe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153737M6UWl78ZRexIcrDs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}